text: Gertrude Appleyard was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 22 April 1865 and died on 9 June 1917. Appleyard competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Gertrude AppleyardGertrude APPLEYARD == References == Category:1865 births Category:1917 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
